From 3fed25019f1ea84d81a01214a148ae03bd8fabbe Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Aaron Liu <aaron.liu@amd.com>
Date: Mon, 23 Aug 2021 12:26:50 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 267/888] drm/amd/display: setup system context for APUs

Scatter/gather is APU feature starting from carrizo.
adev->apu_flags is not used for all APUs.
adev->flags & AMD_IS_APU can be used for all APUs.

Signed-off-by: Aaron Liu <aaron.liu@amd.com>
Reviewed-by: Huang Rui <ray.huang@amd.com>
Signed-off-by: Alex Deucher <alexander.deucher@amd.com>
Cc: stable@vger.kernel.org
---
 drivers/gpu/drm/amd/display/amdgpu_dm/amdgpu_dm.c | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/display/amdgpu_dm/amdgpu_dm.c b/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/display/amdgpu_dm/amdgpu_dm.c
index a90603c7215f..7c746207c033 100644
--- a/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/display/amdgpu_dm/amdgpu_dm.c
+++ b/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/display/amdgpu_dm/amdgpu_dm.c
@@ -1201,7 +1201,7 @@ static int amdgpu_dm_init(struct amdgpu_device *adev)
 	dc_hardware_init(adev->dm.dc);
 
 #if defined(CONFIG_DRM_AMD_DC_DCN)
-	if (adev->apu_flags) {
+	if ((adev->flags & AMD_IS_APU) && (adev->asic_type >= CHIP_CARRIZO)) {
 		struct dc_phy_addr_space_config pa_config;
 
 		mmhub_read_system_context(adev, &pa_config);
-- 
